title: Did Nancy Belusi "Dmit " begin to accuse two years ago?
subtitle: The President of the United States House of Representatives, Nancy Belucci, seemed to confuse the beginning of the investigation with Mueller on the indictment schedule.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The President of the United States House of Representatives, Nancy Pelosi, "Accepted" began the isolation proceedings against President Donald Trump two and a half years ago.
